data.description: Why wait to build? This stunning, luxuriously appointed 2,735 sq.ft. (3,800 total sq.ft.) executive/estate home awaits its new owner now! Located in the gorgeous gated community of Serengeti, this majestic home was built in 2023 and features 3 spacious bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, a flex room which can serve as a formal dining room or home office, an open concept family room with a beautiful center island kitchen including an additional dining area, and an in-law suite complete with its own private living quarters or a possible 4th bedroom. From the luxury vinyl wide plank flooring, ceramic tile, coffered ceilings, wainscoting, plantation shutters, custom designer interior paint, crown moldings, quartz and granite counters, additional wooden kitchen cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, glass tile backsplash, luxurious fixtures including retractable ceiling fans, wet bar and wine fridge in the in-law suite, tinted windows, rain gutters, pavers, and wrought iron fencing, the original owner spared no expense and it shows! Did I mention the amazing view of the pond from the screened-in patio with 16-foot sliders and pavers?! Serengeti is a gated community in Spring Hill, Florida (Pasco County), located approximately 20 minutes North of Tampa. It is conveniently located within minutes of the Suncoast Parkway and the Veterans Expressway, and has 150 acres of natural beauty and wildlife. The community features beautifully designed estate homes on oversized lots up to one acre each. Upon entering the Serengeti community, you will pass an elegant natural stone gateway and will be met with lush landscaping, wooden bridges, and pristine wetland conservation areas. This community offers the opportunity to live in a quiet, peaceful, natural setting within close proximity to downtown Tampa, Clearwater, St. Petersburg, and some of the best beaches in the country! Prime location close to restaurants, shopping, medical facilities, Tampa International Airport. NO CDD FEES. Come and see!
